sources.title: The Lifeguard (Free Full Movie) Drama, Romance, Kristen Bell | 2013 | Sundance selection
sources.description:
A former valedictorian quits her reporter job in New York and returns to the place she last felt happy: her childhood home in Connecticut. She gets work as a lifeguard and starts a dangerous relationship with a troubled teenager.

Premiered as part of the 2013 Sundance Film Festival

Directed by Liz W. Garcia
2013
Starring Kristen Bell, David Lambert, Mamie Gummer, Martin Starr, Joshua Harto, Amy Madigan
